{"tid":1033463,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想買部二手車，想巴打幫幫手","createTime":"2019-02-23T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:33:40.000Z","uid":1724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"05cd4facfeff8b72915249a54506a7f412ec3b36","tid":1033463,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打<br />\n小弟諗住買部二手車星期六日揸<br />\n主要都係車老婆同一個小朋友<br />\nBudget 100K-150K<br />\n<br />\n上28Car睇左幾日<br />\n覺得呢幾部車唔錯<br />\n年份都係2012年左右<br />\nBMW 316i<br />\nBMW 120i<br />\nToyota Camry<br />\n<br />\n如果考慮維修費用，安全，控制<br />\n邊一部會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d736b0aa081a6a0955daa7fc1f7bcb2c91e5dbad","tid":1033463,"uid":41784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"2011 打後bmw 520I"},{"pid":"bc2bbb5ccda13786b77651cdb71519186e0965c8","tid":1033463,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d736b0aa081a6a0955daa7fc1f7bcb2c91e5dbad","tid":1033463,"uid":41784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"2011 打後bmw 520I"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打幫手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔係咁中意5系個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2b2b1a58e5853e536d82a0e48b3b46aba679b7","tid":1033463,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"camry少鑊氣，馬好玩啲<br />\n脷申：馬迷"},{"pid":"6dfc93445699c9be38db9a922f1d21e3e7f89c98","tid":1033463,"uid":172244,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"AE110"},{"pid":"a1093e2f2da1560b90b2466234c924e75e59bd45","tid":1033463,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa2b2b1a58e5853e536d82a0e